{"tid":1323610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣遊行可以繼續由銅鑼灣行去金鐘, 不阻礙自由活動","createTime":"2019-07-16T09:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:55:54.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"79137f9f506bafd6183a3328e1f9b4d5e6dc6a67","tid":1323610,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"和理非遊行好講象徵意義. &nbsp;<br />\n遊行大部份人都唔係常客, 點同佢地解釋點解要由金鐘行去銅鑼灣?<br />\n<br />\n而且, 銅鑼灣行去金鐘, 都不會阻礙自由活動.  我諗71果時, 唔少運登仔都無跟遊行隊, 自由活動, 都無咩大問題.<br />\n<br />\n和理非同自由行繼續發揮民間智慧, 相信唔會出問題. &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/JqmOToN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqmOToN.jpg&h=d31530e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c540fc2a31d37b79ba0eaa1cad2e02f825112f6","tid":1323610,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"just my opinion"},{"pid":"79ada1d8cc57a45adeddb46c84516fbb44ccd104","tid":1323610,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"民陣申請在星期日晚上在金鐘政府總部外集會，要求政府成立獨立調查委員會。民陣下午和警察開會，警方稱基於公共安全考慮，建議將集會改期至8月。民陣表明拒絕，提出反建議在20或21日改為由銅鑼灣遊行到金鐘或中環。召集人岑子杰見記者強調，將集會改為遊行，已是提供彈性予警方考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065728&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTefrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=2e21b477\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065728&h=d2f04d29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065728</a>"}]}